annotationA: L(1)10Bb protein; It is involved in the biological process described with: neurogenesis; mRNA splicing, via spliceosome
annotationB: Pre-mRNA-splicing factor Slu7; Participates in the second catalytic step of pre-mRNA splicing, when the free hydroxyl group of exon I attacks the 3'- splice site to generate spliced mRNA and the excised lariat intron
